  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That's what I found out from I-- and that's what I say, when I mentioned it before, how people were sorry and cried when she passed away.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then also, after that, my daddy-- he tried to-- the life turned to horror.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, in the beginning, we didn't know as much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They told us to wear a white band with a star.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That time, we start to be marked like a-- as a-- only one word, for crime, something we never commit, being a Jew, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we really start to say-- and I remember that in the beginning, when they gave us some leaflet, which being a youngster, I didn't realize, literally, what this-- what the words meant.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There are so many countries, so much-- so many lands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And for us, there's no room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To us, we just repeated, like a-- something we couldn't observe in our mind, that something could be so strange to us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Finally, when they start-- and every day, they start to hear-- they systematically [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Sometimes, they grabbed young people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Sometimes boys from the street-- they disappeared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They didn't know where they went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So naturally, the parents start to worry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they start to-- every day, somewhere else to try to hide.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I was one night-- first of all, about my brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
